Vacancy Identification Number (VIN) 1811627, please write on all documents with application.&#160;One (1)&#160;vacancy exists in Gainesville,&#160;Florida for a&#160;Health Science Specialist in&#160;Research Service,&#160;at&#160;North Florida/South Georgia Veterans Health System (NF/SG VHS).&#160;NOTE:&#160; THIS IS A&#160;TIME-LIMITED APPOINTMENT NOT-TO-EXCEED FRIDAY, JUNE 30, 2017, WITH THE ABILITY TO BE EXTENDED OUT&#160;IN THREE (3) YEAR INCREMENTS&#160;UPON AVAILABLE FUNDING.&#160; THIS POSITION IS SUBJECT TO TERMS OF TEMPORARY EMPLOYMENT AND MAY BE TERMINATED AT ANY TIME DUE TO LACK OF FUNDING OR AT THE FACILITIES DISCRETION.
